I defined four teams whose source is a single board. Each team is set up for two week sprints. When I try to remove the grouping on the schedule view, I get the attached error. Unchecking "Sprints" brings the issues back, which still seem to be grouped by sprint -- only the sprint name is omitted. Why does it think that my teams aren't on the same schedule?

